1.
 Purpose
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\lang english
This policy governs the packaging,
 testing,
 and deployment of applications,
 drivers,
 firmware,
 and associated documentation to production environments within the Elko County Information Operations Department (ECIO).
\end_layout

