6.9 Vendor Cloud Deployments
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\lang english
Where a vendor deployment in a cloud environment that ECIO does not directly control affects County-managed systems,
 the Information Operations Personnel who discovers the change shall notify the IT Director or Assistant IT Director upon discovery.
 The Assistant IT Director shall document the notification and assess the impact within one (1) business day of receipt.
